  "overallFindings": {
    "expeditionNotes": "Bolt pattern transition from 5x135 (1997-2002) to 6x135 (2003+) is correctly captured. Hub bore 87.1mm consistent across all years. Wheel/tire sizes align with OEM specifications.",
    "explorerNotes": "Bolt pattern 5x114.3 consistent across all generations. Hub bore correctly shows transition from 70.5mm (pre-2011) to 63.4mm (2011-2019). 2020+ hub bore is disputed - batch has 63.4mm but some sources indicate return to 70.5mm for 6th gen. Flagging 2020+ for manual review.",
    "sportTracNotes": "ALL Explorer Sport Trac entries have INVALID tire sizes. The batch shows 205/55R16 which is a passenger car tire - completely wrong for this truck-based vehicle. Correct sizes are 235/75R15, 255/70R16 (2001-2005) and 235/70R16, 245/65R17, etc. (2007-2010). Wheel specs for 2007-2010 are correct."
  },
